Blacknightmare:

"We arrived, Orchestra" said the femme showing the cr's "Now take one 
and rest, you deserve it..."

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "dcoburn" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra/Decapitron/Legtrap/Headshot::
> 
>       Orchestra smiled and walked beside Blacknightmare, hand in 
hand.  His knee and elbow plating were scratched from skidding on the 
ground, and some of the rest of his armor was damaged.  Orchestra had 
been standing near Darkfate when Unicron fired some missiles.  The 
explosion sent Orchestra flying back, and he sort of spiraled, and 
landed face first, then skidded a bit.  They were almost at the CR 
Chambers.
